Rowdy Wolf:







Rowdy Wolf paused. Maximals...

He lowered his head. "I was originally a Maximal. Quickstrike turned me into 
a Predacon. He never did it by force. It made him mad when I showed him what 
I was. I have never met another bot since I was out here." He put his rifle 
behind his back, under his armor.
